""SELECT f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\" AS \"ProvinceName\", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT t4.\"FarmId\"
        FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t3 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t3.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON t3.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p0 ON f0.\"ProvinceId\" = p0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t4 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t4.\"Id\"
        WHERE NOT (t1.\"Deleted\") AND t3.\"IsActive\" AND f.\"ProvinceId\" = f0.\"ProvinceId\" AND p.\"Name\" = p0.\"Name\"
    ) AS t2) AS \"FarmCount\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) AS \"CompletedHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\", CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) / COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0)) * 100
    ELSE 0
END AS \"CompletionPercentage\"
FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p ON f.\"ProvinceId\" = p.\"Id\"
WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) DESC"
2025-08-06T08:33:40.7267790+02:00 [INF] (Hurudza.Services.Core) Executed DbCommand ("3"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\", COALESCE(sum(t1.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"HectaresCompleted\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t1.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"Revenue\", count(*)::int AS \"ServicesCompleted\"
FROM (
    SELECT t.\"Hectares\", t.\"ServiceCost\", date_part('year', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Year\", date_part('month', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Month\"
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
    INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
    WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"IsCompleted\"
) AS t1
GROUP BY t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\"
ORDER BY t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\""

2025-08-06T08:37:58.4716450+02:00 [INF] (Hurudza.Services.Core) Executed DbCommand ("49"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\" AS \"ProvinceName\", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT t4.\"FarmId\"
        FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t3 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t3.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON t3.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p0 ON f0.\"ProvinceId\" = p0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t4 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t4.\"Id\"
        WHERE NOT (t1.\"Deleted\") AND t3.\"IsActive\" AND f.\"ProvinceId\" = f0.\"ProvinceId\" AND p.\"Name\" = p0.\"Name\"
    ) AS t2) AS \"FarmCount\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) AS \"CompletedHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\", CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) / COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0)) * 100
    ELSE 0
END AS \"CompletionPercentage\"
FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p ON f.\"ProvinceId\" = p.\"Id\"
WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) DESC"

""SELECT t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\", COALESCE(sum(t1.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"HectaresCompleted\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t1.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"Revenue\", count(*)::int AS \"ServicesCompleted\"
FROM (
    SELECT t.\"Hectares\", t.\"ServiceCost\", date_part('year', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Year\", date_part('month', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Month\"
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
    INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
    WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"IsCompleted\"
) AS t1
GROUP BY t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\"
ORDER BY t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\""

""SELECT t.\"TillageType\", count(*)::int AS \"Count\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"

2025-08-06T08:55:25.2884440+02:00 [INF] (Hurudza.Services.Core) Executed DbCommand ("6"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\" AS \"ProvinceName\", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT t4.\"FarmId\"
        FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t3 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t3.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON t3.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p0 ON f0.\"ProvinceId\" = p0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t4 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t4.\"Id\"
        WHERE NOT (t1.\"Deleted\") AND t3.\"IsActive\" AND f.\"ProvinceId\" = f0.\"ProvinceId\" AND p.\"Name\" = p0.\"Name\"
    ) AS t2) AS \"FarmCount\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) AS \"CompletedHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\", CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) / COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0)) * 100
    ELSE 0
END AS \"CompletionPercentage\"
FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p ON f.\"ProvinceId\" = p.\"Id\"

""SELECT t1.\"Year\", t1.\"Month\", COALESCE(sum(t1.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"HectaresCompleted\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t1.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"Revenue\", count(*)::int AS \"ServicesCompleted\"
FROM (
    SELECT t.\"Hectares\", t.\"ServiceCost\", date_part('year', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Year\", date_part('month', t.\"ServiceDate\")::int AS \"Month\"
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
    INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
    WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"IsCompleted\"

""SELECT t.\"Id\", t.\"Name\", t.\"Size\", t.\"Arable\", t.\"Cleared\", t.\"Terrain\", t.\"Latitude\", t.\"Longitude\", t.\"SoilType\", t0.\"Name\", t0.\"Description\", t0.\"SoilType\", t0.\"Irrigation\", t0.\"Size\", t0.\"FarmId\", t0.\"Name0\", t0.\"Id\", t0.\"Id0\", t0.\"FieldId\", t0.\"Id1\", t0.\"CreatedDate\", t0.\"CreatorId\", t0.\"Deleted\", t0.\"Description0\", t0.\"FarmId0\", t0.\"Irrigation0\", t0.\"IsActive\", t0.\"IsArchived\", t0.\"ModifiedBy\", t0.\"Name1\", t0.\"Size0\", t0.\"SoilType0\", t0.\"UpdatedAt\", t0.\"Version\", t0.\"Label\", t0.\"Longitude\", t0.\"Latitude\", t0.\"Altitude\", t0.\"Id00\", t0.\"UpdatedAt0\", t0.\"Deleted0\", t0.\"CreatedDate0\", t0.\"CreatorId0\", t0.\"ModifiedBy0\", t0.\"IsArchived0\", t0.\"IsActive0\", t0.\"UpdatedAt1\", t0.\"Deleted1\", t0.\"CreatedDate1\", t0.\"CreatorId1\", t0.\"ModifiedBy1\", t0.\"IsArchived1\", t0.\"IsActive1\", t.\"UpdatedAt\", t.\"Deleted\", t.\"CreatedDate\", t.\"CreatorId\", t.\"ModifiedBy\", t.\"IsArchived\", t.\"IsActive\", t2.\"Longitude\", t2.\"Latitude\", t2.\"Id\"
FROM (
    SELECT f.\"Id\", f.\"Name\", f.\"Size\", f.\"Arable\", f.\"Cleared\", f.\"Terrain\", f.\"Latitude\", f.\"Longitude\", f.\"SoilType\", f.\"UpdatedAt\", f.\"Deleted\", f.\"CreatedDate\", f.\"CreatorId\", f.\"ModifiedBy\", f.\"IsArchived\", f.\"IsActive\"
    FROM \"Farms\" AS f
    WHERE f.\"Id\" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0.\"Name\", f0.\"Description\", f0.\"SoilType\", f0.\"Irrigation\", f0.\"Size\", f0.\"FarmId\", f1.\"Name\" AS \"Name0\", f0.\"Id\", f1.\"Id\" AS \"Id0\", t1.\"FieldId\", t1.\"Id\" AS \"Id1\", t1.\"CreatedDate\", t1.\"CreatorId\", t1.\"Deleted\", t1.\"Description\" AS \"Description0\", t1.\"FarmId\" AS \"FarmId0\", t1.\"Irrigation\" AS \"Irrigation0\", t1.\"IsActive\", t1.\"IsArchived\", t1.\"ModifiedBy\", t1.\"Name\" AS \"Name1\", t1.\"Size\" AS \"Size0\", t1.\"SoilType\" AS \"SoilType0\", t1.\"UpdatedAt\", t1.\"Version\", t1.\"Label\", t1.\"Longitude\", t1.\"Latitude\", t1.\"Altitude\", t1.\"Id0\" AS \"Id00\", t1.\"UpdatedAt0\", t1.\"Deleted0\", t1.\"CreatedDate0\", t1.\"CreatorId0\", t1.\"ModifiedBy0\", t1.\"IsArchived0\", t1.\"IsActive0\", f0.\"UpdatedAt\" AS \"UpdatedAt1\", f0.\"Deleted\" AS \"Deleted1\", f0.\"CreatedDate\" AS \"CreatedDate1\", f0.\"CreatorId\" AS \"CreatorId1\", f0.\"ModifiedBy\" AS \"ModifiedBy1\", f0.\"IsArchived\" AS \"IsArchived1\", f0.\"IsActive\" AS \"IsActive1\"
    FROM \"Fields\" AS f0
    INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f1 ON f0.\"FarmId\" = f1.\"Id\"
    LEFT JOIN (

    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"

    WHERE t0.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"FarmId\" = t0.\"FarmId\"
    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"

    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"

""SELECT f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\" AS \"ProvinceName\", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT t4.\"FarmId\"
        FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t3 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t3.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON t3.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p0 ON f0.\"ProvinceId\" = p0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t4 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t4.\"Id\"
        WHERE NOT (t1.\"Deleted\") AND t3.\"IsActive\" AND f.\"ProvinceId\" = f0.\"ProvinceId\" AND p.\"Name\" = p0.\"Name\"
    ) AS t2) AS \"FarmCount\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) AS \"CompletedHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\", CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) / COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0)) * 100
    ELSE 0
END AS \"CompletionPercentage\"
FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p ON f.\"ProvinceId\" = p.\"Id\"
WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) DESC"

""SELECT t.\"FarmId\", (
    SELECT f.\"Name\"
    FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0
    INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
    WHERE t0.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t0.\"IsActive\" AND t.\"FarmId\" = t0.\"FarmId\"
    LIMIT 1) AS \"FarmName\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TotalHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalPlanned\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"TilledHectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalTilled\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((

    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"
